   <text type="letter">
      <body>
         
            <opener rend="right">
               <dateline>
                  <name type="place">Department of the Interior,<lb/>
Washington,</name>
                  <date when="1865-01-12">January 12, 1865.</date>
               </dateline>
               <salute>Sir:</salute>
            </opener>
            <p>Upon reporting at this Department and passing a satisfactory examination you will be appointed to a First Class Clerkship at a compensation of twelve hundred dollars per annum.<ptr target="nyp.00219_n2"/> I am, Sir, very respectfully, your obt servant</p>  
            <closer rend="right">
               <signed>W. T. Otto, Assistant Secretary.<ptr target="nyp.00219_n100"/>
            </signed>
            </closer>
         
         <postscript>
            <p>Walt Whitman, Esq.<lb/>
Brooklyn, N. Y.</p>
         </postscript>
      </body>
